data.description: Beautiful 5 bedroom, 2 bath, 2,398sf Oak Lawn 2 story home with an addition! This incredibly spacious home features a sun-filled living room, large eat in kitchen with granite countertops, oak cabinetry, pantry, and island. The main level has two bedrooms, an inviting family room, a den with closet (could be a 6th bedroom), a full bathroom with tub/shower combination, convenient main level laundry room with multiple storage cabinets and utility sink. The second level features three huge bedrooms with large closets and a full bathroom with walk in shower. Zoned HVAC! The den was previously a one car garage. Nice newer concrete side drive could hold 2-3 vehicles. The fully privacy yard has a screened in porch, shed and lots of green space! The property taxes are $5,961.57 per year with the Homeowner and Senior Exemptions (based on certificate of error filed and documented under additional information). Great location near the Metra, downtown Oak Lawn, library, parks, Children's Museum, Covington Elementary School, Christ Hospital and quick access to I-294!
